OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and early outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain soon clear north to leave bright
OL,7,Fspells which will be interspersed with
OL,8,Fblustery showers, some heavy. Strong
OL,9,Fsoutheasterly winds with coastal gales.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe mix of clear spells and
OL,12,Fblustery showers will continue through
OL,13,Fthe night. The strong southeasterly
OL,14,Fwind and coastal gales will decrease,
OL,15,Fturning fresh southerly towards the
OL,16,Fmorning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FThe showers will clear during
OL,19,Fthe morning to leave the afternoon dry
OL,20,Fwith increasing sunny spells over
OL,21,FShetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
