OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday. Cloud and
OL,7,Frain spread northeast Wednesday,
OL,8,Fclearing north Wednesday night.
OL,9,FShowers follow from the south Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
